creator: Ready Education
descriptionHtml:
The LTCC Coyote Corner App brings services to your fingertips and enables you to connect with classmates and friends. Access events, calendars, contacts, maps and more! Stay organized with the timetable function, where you can save events, classes and assignments.
Features that help with student life:
+ Classes: Manage classes, create to-dos & reminders, and stay on top of assignments.
+ Groups & Clubs: How to get involved with campus clubs.
+ Campus Resources: Connect with programs on campus such as Equity, Veterans, Financial Aid, EOPS, etc.
+ Events: See what events are happening on campus.
+ Tour: Explore the campus.
+ Campus Services: Learn about services offered.
+ Campus Feed: Join the campus discussion.
+ Campus Map: Directions to classes, events and offices.
descriptionShort: The LTCC Coyote Corner app connects you to student life & campus resources

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We improve the app for our users with bi-weekly updates to add new features, squash bugs and improve app performance. We'd love to hear from you if you have any feedback for us.

descriptionHtml:
The Coyote Corner App brings services to your fingertips and enables you to connect with classmates and friends. Access events, calendars, contacts, maps and more! Stay organized with the timetable function, where you can save events, classes and assignments.
Features that help with student life:
+ Classes: Manage classes, create to-dos & reminders, and stay on top of assignments.
+ Groups & Clubs: How to get involved with campus clubs.
+ Campus Resources: Connect with programs on campus such as Equity, Veterans, Financial Aid, EOPS, etc.
+ Events: See what events are happening on campus.
+ Tour: Explore the campus.
+ Campus Services: Learn about services offered.
+ Campus Feed: Join the campus discussion.
+ Campus Map: Directions to classes, events and offices.
descriptionShort: The LTCC Coyote Corner app connects you to student life & campus resources
